    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 guidance for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB flow envelope described in the bound claim and requirement records. No unresolved weakeners identified.",
